WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:10.000
 Separate Bike and Zigo Leader Stroller 

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
 Activate the parking brake (tighten the Jogging brake lever and press stop) 

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:30.000
 Lower both adjustable front wheels (release the Velcro and press the buttons inside) 

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:40.000
 Release the LeaderLink brake (the knob should rise freely) 

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:49.000
 Release the stroller anchorage clip on the bike 

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:53.000
 Pull the bike away from the stroller upright 

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:57.000
 Lower the stand and leave the bike on the side 

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
 Reposition the push bar back (hold both buttons simultaneously) 

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:08.000
 Release the parking brake (tighten the Jogging brake lever) 

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:12.000
 Activate the steering lock (pull the knob away from the stroller and turn it clockwise) 

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.000
 To recap ... 

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:21.000
 Set the parking brake 

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:29.000
 Lower both casters 

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:42.000
 Release the LeaderLink brake 

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:48.000
 Release the anchor catch 

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:51.000
 Pull the bike away from the riser 

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.000
 Lower the stand 

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:59.000
 Ensures the anchorage stop 

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:06.000
 Reposition the push bar back 

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:09.000
 Release the parking brake 

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:14.000
 Activate the steering lock 

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:22.000
